  home:['Edit the homepage title, summary and sections. Drag sections to change their order. Save Draft keeps changes private; Publish makes them live.','Homepage changes appear after Publish. Use Preview to open the live homepage in a new tab.'],
  about:['Edit the About content in both languages. Save each section, then Publish the page when it is ready.','The About section on the homepage reads this published content.'],
